author: ForrestKnight
description:
Java 24 brings major performance and usability upgrades to the world’s most widely used enterprise programming language. Learn how Ahead-of-Time Class Loading, Stream Gatherers, Virtual Thread fixes, Pattern Matching improvements, and the removal of Security Manager make Java faster and more efficient than ever.
